---
title: Ricotta Rigatoni and Shrimp Al Forno with Spinach and Mozzarella
description: Just like Nonna's pasta al forno, this rigatoni bake is overflowing with cheese and shrimp! Creamy ricotta and gooey mozzarella give this dish its rich deliciousness, while wholesome baby spinach adds a pop of bright, fresh flavour.
